<task id="task_7867C3B8F2DB44B9A0965F23E1AAC43C" xml:lang="en-us">
    <title>Integrating with <ph conref="../../Shared/Product_Name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
        /> Event Management</title>
    <taskbody>
        <context>
            <p id="The_event_management_service_task_taskbody_context_p_1">The event management service in <ph
                    conref="../../Shared/Product_Name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                /> collects specific events generated during application operation. These events can be used for price models, billing, and reporting. Examples of events are the completion of a specific transaction, or the creation or deletion of specific data.</p>
            <p id="Your_application_can_send_eve_task_taskbody_context_p_2">Your application can send events to <ph
                    conref="../../Shared/Product_Name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                    /> at runtime through the event management service, which is one of the <ph
                    conref="../../Shared/Product_Name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"/> platform services. </p>
            <p id="comes_with_two_predefined_ev_task_taskbody_context_p_2">To integrate with <ph
                    conref="../../Shared/Product_Name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"/> event management:</p>
        </context>
        <steps>
            <step>
                <cmd>If your application does not generate the required events yet, implement the generation of events.</cmd>
            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd>Implement the sending of events to <ph
                        conref="../../Shared/Product_Name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"/>.</cmd>
                <!--info>
                    <p>For details, refer to the <i>Developer's Guide</i>.</p>
                </info-->
            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd id="When_preparing_the_service_de_task_taskbody_steps_step_3"
                    >When preparing the technical service definition, declare the events that your application will send. </cmd>
                <info>
                    <p audience="doc">For details on the technical service definition, refer to <xref
                            href="../../TechProvGuide/Reference/r_TechServDescr.xml"
                            ><?xm-replace_text xref: "Service Definition Reference"?></xref>. </p>
                </info>
            </step>
        </steps>
    </taskbody>
</task>
